// Handles instant student field updates via WhatsApp command
//
// Format 1 — Update by field value (existing):
//   Update_FieldName_OldValue into NewValue
//
// Format 2 — Update by Register Number (NEW):
//   Update_RegisterNumber_FieldName into NewValue
//
// Examples:
//   Update_Section_N/A into B              ← by old value
//   Update_922523205002_Section into B     ← by reg number ✅
//   Update_922523205002_CGPA into 8.5      ← by reg number ✅
//   Update_922523205002_Mobile into 9876543210

